title: 1965 / 66 Season Poster for the Municipal Theater, Basel, with Weekly Program [Saisonplakat Stadttheater, Basel mit Wochenspielplan]
medium: Offset lithograph on white wove paper
description: Photographic reproductions of a Classical column, a boot with a spur, a ballet dancer's leg en pointe, a music stand, a quarter of a cello. In upper left quadrant, the following inscription in black letters: Stadt / Theater / Basel / 1965 / 66.
name: Poster
